description:
Hi Friends,

#SellingLeaders uses a simple email template that you can use to meet almost anyone. I have a book coming in the fall by the same name. I will continue to update the course with new material as I have recently been creating a ton of new content. Look forward to support and accessibility. I want you to succeed. The first step is to send emails. Anyone can do it.

Your Coach-On-Demand,

Mark Latimer
title: How to Win Time with Busy People by: Mark Latimer
